@startuml 04-rolling-deploy-sequence
skinparam dpi 300
title Problem 4 — Rolling-Deploy Churn / Handoff vs. Grace (CoEdit)

participant "Deployment\ncontroller" as Dep
participant "kubelet" as Kubelet
participant "pod-2 BEAM\n(400 doc procs)" as P2
participant "Phoenix\nEndpoint" as EP
participant "Horde" as Horde
participant "surviving\nnode" as Surv
actor Client

Dep -> Kubelet: rolling update -> terminate pod-2
Kubelet -> P2: SIGTERM
note right of Kubelet: terminationGracePeriodSeconds = 30
P2 -> P2: trap SIGTERM
P2 -> EP: drain (stop accepting)
P2 -> Horde: hand off 400 doc processes

loop each document (serialize + transfer CRDT)
  Horde -> Surv: transfer doc state
end
note over Horde,Surv #ffcccc: handoff takes ~45s under load

Kubelet -> P2: SIGKILL (at t = 30s)
note over P2 #ffcccc: ~150 docs not yet moved\ndie with unsynced edits

Client -> Surv: reconnect
Surv --> Client: doc missing recent edits
@enduml
